### GET all patients
GET http://localhost:3001/api/patients
Accept: application/json

###

### POST a new patient (correct data)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Smith",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-05-15",
  "ssn": "123-45-6789",
  "gender": "female",
  "occupation": "Engineer"
}

###

### POST a new patient (invalid data)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Jones",
  "dateOfBirth": "not-a-date",
  "ssn": "987-65-4321",
  "gender": "unknown",
  "occupation": "Pilot"
}
